# PostgreSQL CODEOWNERS
# 此文件定义哪些用户应该审查特定代码区域的更改
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# 默认审查者（所有更改）
* @core-team

# 后端核心模块
/src/backend/access/ @backend-access-team
/src/backend/catalog/ @backend-catalog-team
/src/backend/executor/ @backend-executor-team
/src/backend/optimizer/ @backend-optimizer-team
/src/backend/parser/ @backend-parser-team
/src/backend/planner/ @backend-planner-team
/src/backend/storage/ @backend-storage-team
/src/backend/utils/ @backend-utils-team

# 特定功能区域
/src/backend/replication/ @replication-team
/src/backend/foreign/ @foreign-data-team
/src/backend/tsearch/ @tsearch-team

# 接口和工具
/src/bin/ @tools-team
/src/interfaces/libpq/ @libpq-team
/src/interfaces/ecpg/ @ecpg-team

# 文档
/doc/ @doc-team *.md

# 构建系统
/GNUmakefile.in @build-team
/Makefile* @build-team
/configure* @build-team
/src/Makefile.global.in @build-team

# 配置和平台特定
/src/port/ @platform-team
/src/template/ @platform-team
/src/makefiles/ @build-team

# 本文件本身
/CODEOWNERS @project-lead

# AI 审查配置（任何修改都需要审查）
/.github/copilot-instructions.md @code-review-team
/.github/workflows/ai-review.yml @code-review-team
/.github/agents/ @code-review-team
